---

<BaseLayout
  title="Martial Arts Scheduling Software (2026) - Class Booking & Capacity Management"
  description="Automate class scheduling for martial arts schools. Student self-service booking, belt-based restrictions, automated reminders, waitlist management, and instructor coordination. Reduce no-shows by 58% and admin time by 12+ hours weekly."
>
  <BreadcrumbsEnhanced site="mydojo" items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
